{
  "stem": "15694.10",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "I just wanted-- my father had just stepped onto one of the wagons, and I saw a number of kapos going into a different-- to the front of the train.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And some of them carrying, carrying parcels, some of them carrying mattress, mattresses.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And I, with a unfilial jerk, I pulled my father from the train again.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And we went after them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "It was going into the lion's den, but we were lucky before.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "So we found ourselves in the middle of a wagon with kapos.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Never.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Probably, they didn't either.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they made themselves, you know, mattresses and food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm sure they had enough.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was the first wagon in a long train.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And as we went, as we stepped into the wagon, helping out to lay out the mattresses, one of the, some of the kapos shushed away other prisoners who wanted to get on.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Away!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then the doors closed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And a voice said to me, what are you doing here?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Out!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] You can throw me out but not alive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I stood.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I knew my father would stand behind me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he looked around, and somebody sort of waved him off.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were, the two of us, amongst other 36 kapos, most of them, I'm sure, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] besties, beasts.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] But, actually, they had no more-- at that time they were prisoners.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Their function had ended.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But soon, although I had-- we were-- the wagon was full of blankets, of mattresses-- we're lying, sleeping, eating, everything on blankets-- but we're only 38.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we could stretch out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And really lie down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And at night we slept under a layer of blankets.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
